      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, likely best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust patches on the wheel arches and rocker panels, along with faded paint and a cracked windshield. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will require immediate attention, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the fabric, and some electronic components, such as the radio and rear power windows, are non-functional. Please expect to invest time and resources into significant repairs to make this vehicle roadworthy again.",
