      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common floor fatigue, and the dual-VANOS system has been recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque across the rev range. Suspension components maintain factory kinematics with refreshed bushings, offering the balanced handling and tactile steering feedback this chassis is known for. A mechanically robust performance machine with a clean title and documented service history.",
